cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CE 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for solving three important topics in the area of urban air computing, namely interpolation, prediction, and feature analysis of fine-grained air quality. The proposed approach utilizes feature selection and semi-supervised learning in different layers of the deep learning network. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval)
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks)
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science)
